title: I haven't recieved any icons recently?
body: So, I haven't recieved any icons recently! I did the Star Guardian quiz and I didn't get the icon? Everyone got some sort of poro icon, if I remember correctly. That's basically it. Thanks in advance to anyone who can help!

replies.body: I don't believe that the star guardian icons are benig distributed anymore.  Only poro icon I can think of is for Worlds Pick Em.  If you haven't received one submit a [support ticket](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new) and we can take a look.  I highly recommend taking screenshots of those pages while logged in to help advocate.  We'll reply asap!
